The paper proposes a novel approach for handling loop vectorization using deep reinforcement learning. This involves developing an end-to-end framework that integrates deep RL in the LLVM compiler. The paper also mentions the use of supervised learning methods. Based on this, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.PL (Programming Languages), cs.AR (Hardware Architecture), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
